<h4 class="wp-block-heading">How To Do</h4>



<ol>
<li>Sit on the preacher bench and place your upper arms on the pad. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with palms facing up.</li>



<li>Curl the dumbbells up towards your shoulders, keeping your upper arms stationary.</li>



<li>As you reach the top of the curl, rotate your wrists so your palms face downward.</li>



<li>Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the start position with your palms facing down.</li>



<li>Rotate your wrists back to the starting position, with palms facing up, to complete the rep.</li>



<li>Perform the desired number of repetitions, maintaining control and proper form throughout.</li>
</ol>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-incline-bicep-curl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Dumbbell Incline Bicep Curl</a></h3>



