<h4 class="wp-block-heading">How To Do</h4>



<ol>
<li>Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart.</li>



<li>Hold a dumbbell in each hand near your thighs.</li>



<li>Take a deep breath in and brace your core. Lift the dumbbells in front of you to shoulder level, with your palms facing the ground.</li>



<li>Hold the top position with your shoulders engaged and core braced.</li>



<li>Exhale as you slowly lower the dumbbells back to the start under control.</li>



<li>Repeat as needed.</li>
</ol>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-reverse-fly" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Dumbbell Reverse Fly</a></h3>



