<ol>
<li>Grab a dumbbell in your right hand with an overhand grip. Your feet should be hip-width apart. Bring the weight to shoulder level, with your elbow in at your side.</li>



<li>Press the weight overhead to the full lockout of the elbow.</li>



<li>Lower the weight under control to the start position.</li>



<li>Breathe out as you press the weight up; breathe in as you lower the weight.</li>
</ol>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/seated-dumbbell-rear-delt-fly" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Seated Dumbbell Rear Delt Fly</a></h3>



