<li>Hold the dumbbell in your right hand.</li>



<li>Lie down on your stomach on the bench, positioning your chin on the very end.</li>



<li>Bend your knees, keeping your toes on the ground.</li>



<li>Grip the frame of the bench with your left hand.</li>



<li>Allow your working arm to hang down at your side. This is your starting position.</li>



<li>Inhale, engaging the core.</li>



<li>On your exhale, raise your working arm out to the side until it is parallel to the floor.</li>



<li>Inhale and return to the starting position.</li>
